list-item.p:
The juice or tea of 
   Citrus limon (L.) Burm.f fruits, alone or associated with salt, honey or ginger has been used to relieve cough and fever related to flu and cold in several traditional systems (
   Papp et al., 2011; 
   Panizza et al., 2012; 
   Sultana et al., 2016; 
   Klimek-Szczykutowicz et al., 2020). However, there is no clinical evidence of such action in the respiratory tract, although this species is well-known as a rich source of vitamin C (
   Ye, 2017).
